01:11:04.310 --> 01:11:04.330
If you hadn't thought
about this material before,

01:11:04.330 --> 01:11:04.760
you need to think about this stuff,
because it makes a difference.

01:11:04.760 --> 01:11:05.160
Because it makes a difference.

01:11:05.180 --> 01:11:06.950
It's a big difference.

01:11:07.170 --> 01:11:08.680
Performance is measured in two ways.

01:11:08.680 --> 01:11:10.720
I think when you talk to
users about performance,

01:11:10.720 --> 01:11:14.600
